{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"role":"sampleCode","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"roleHeading":"WWDC15","title":"App Extension Best Practices"},"kind":"article","sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"App extensions allow powerful ways to expose your application’s abilities throughout iOS and other apps. Discover best practices for various extension types and see how to effectively communicate between your extension and its parent application or the network. Learn techniques for using the shared keychain and see how to improve discovery of your share and action extensions.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc15-224-app-extension-best-practices"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC15"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","isActive":true}]},{"anchor":"Related-Sessions","text":"Related Sessions","type":"heading","level":2},{"items":["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC16-214-Extending-your-App-with-Safari-App-Extensions","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC16-225-Extending-Your-Apps-with-SiriKit"],"style":"list","type":"links"}]}],"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"isActive":true,"overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex","type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2015\/224\/"}},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/docume